Subject: [PATCH 083/122] mm: madvise(MADV_DODUMP): allow hugetlbfs pages

commit d41aa5252394c065d1f04d1ceea885b70d00c9c6 upstream.

Reproducer, assuming 2M of hugetlbfs available:

